Okay. So, my Aunt Pat lives in Florida, right? And I havent seen her for five years, right? So my grandmother sends monies down there for her, her fiance Richard, Carolyn, and Carolyn's husband Jonathan to come up to Michigan. So, last night, me, mom, and jessie go over to my grandmother's to wait for them. But they dont come until one am and we left at like, eight. So today, after school, we went over there. We talked and talked and then we decided to go to Elkhart, Indiana. Where my uncle Floyd lives. I hadnt went to the bathroom since six this morning. It was six when we left. I had to go to the bathroom soooooo bad, I started crying cause it hurt. We stopped at a gas station maybe, two seconds from my uncle's. When I came out, my aunt was slamming the side of her van and yelling at me to hurry up. Julie decided to tell them that I had peed forever, and that she thought the faucet was on. Jennifer, her two sons, Billy, my uncle, and my aunt were there. My uncle made pizza.  We all shared stories. Then we decided it was time to leave. an hour there and back. and it was eight there. So, we get going and my mom didnt turn where she was supposed to. So she pulls over and decides to turn around. Julie told her there was a car behind Carolyn and moms like, "No that is Carolyn." And the other car almost hit us, then Carolyn turned and was about an inch away from her. We got back to my grandmother's house and said goodbye. then took Carolyn and Jonathan to Carolyn's grandmother's house. then we came back here. Tomorrow we have to take adam over there.
